#USAGE:
	To sign your files, just drag and drop your private key and your file to sign into Singning/Sign folder,
than, get your, private key, signature and file from the ingning/Signed folder.
	To verify a signature, just drag and drop the the respective public key,file signed and signature into the 
Verifying/Verify folder. If the signature is valid, all files will be transfered to Valid-Sign folder, if not,
they will be transferd to Not-Valid-Sign.

#CUTION!
	To prevent bugs, DO NOT sign or verify more than one file at the same time.

	To verify, the public key needs to be correctly called "public-key-file.pem".

	To verify, the signature needs to be correctly called "signature.sig".
